Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:28.15,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(820,660)}Panther
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是戰車！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意義不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是 比如大膽搭配轉輪圖案的這款泳衣..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量採用網格狀布料 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜擼..喜擼什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝甲裙板對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.16,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(590,660)}schurzen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.16,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：二戰末期，配備大幅精簡的四號J型坦克開始採用鐵網狀裝甲裙板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外裝式的輔助裝甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這種款式的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透著一股南國風味 很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個標誌是..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這是非洲軍團式樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個！還有這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連我也要..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這是英國第七裝甲師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:04:02.33,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}M3斯圖亞特輕型坦克：二戰美國研製的一款輕型坦克 主炮 37mm gun M5/M6 \N500米穿深 54/78mm（APC/APCR）最大時速 56km/h 裝甲 26-38mm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通稱“沙漠之鼠”式樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯 我覺得今年一定會流行這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得永遠不會流行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校指定的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的有不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑哪個好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前突然冒出這麼多品種的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了嗎~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇~好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦吼~好可愛好可愛好可愛好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後全開..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這款又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈~這邊也超可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後方注意..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看啊 這個這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DUI的干式潛水衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.64,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}DUI："DIVING UNLIMITED INTERNATIONAL"某專業潛水器材品牌，\N一套CLX450潛水衣折合軟妹幣約18000圓，謝謝惠顧~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豹突擊隊也在用它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼高端還是免了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話又太成人向了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人困擾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明穿學校指定的就好了說..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得更可愛的比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要輕飄飄的或者有花紋的才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕飄飄的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 輕飄飄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕飄飄..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕飄飄的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕飄飄到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣子滴！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正可謂圍裙輕飄飄官爺吃不消！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕飄飄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撇去迷彩以外的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我穿這個就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子這個不對啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有在聽我說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話更紳士一點的更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優花里！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件泳衣是舊款式的死庫水 簡稱舊水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這泳衣的用法還真深不可測呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子 穿這個穿這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷泉同學 這件也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷泉同學快穿上去 很漂亮哦..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看這件 好可愛..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:23.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~嗯~嗯~嗯~嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特種部隊的一整套裝備如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說選個正常點的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件怎麼說呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色兜襠布！紅色兜襠布！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛歷史愛兜襠布！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然該穿六文錢的紅色兜襠布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是非洲軍團式樣的椰子樹圖案比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到羅馬軍團就是甲胄！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有紅圍巾！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:48.46,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}盔甲泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上海援隊的紅白紋才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.14,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}海援隊：江戶時代後期幕末脫藩浪士們以坂本龍馬為中心結成的貿易組織。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真田繩也難以割捨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:51.70,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真田繩：一種用木棉絲織成的平實厚重的線，傳說由真田昌幸·信繁父子製作出來。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是穿由德國開發出來的能溶於水的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的還是這件印有家紋的肚兜泳衣是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的玩法好像很厲害的樣子..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的情況變得有點莫名其妙..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.29,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,577)\frz18}踢水板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的場面感覺好恐怖..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說妳說 這件和這件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一件更可愛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先看我的 這件和這件哪件更適合我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豹突擊隊式樣和英國SBS\N以及法國海軍Commando還有俄羅斯特種部隊..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金泳衣銀泳衣~妳要的是哪一件？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶~是哪件啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都太鬆了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們知不知道羞恥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃桃 說服力為負
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯 這種時候不好好玩怎行呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有在盡興玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這世上還有這麼多種類的泳衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾來點戰車之外的東西也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明穿學校指定的就好了說..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果自己還不是買了件蠻下限的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記買了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是替您買了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？但是尺寸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的三圍目測技能點滿了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸圍82
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰圍56
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臀圍84
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體測量儀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海耶！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備周全了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那開游了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一名~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓給妳~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
